{"tid":1670484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰集會事件，關於solomon表態","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T05:11:58.000Z","uid":29299,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69f3a738753baf11b4a1a76fed1f5cceb1e06069","tid":1670484,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"4個月運動以來，<br />\n點解港府一直解決唔到？<br />\n歸究於無大台同網民自發性遊行/集會<br />\n根本無機會去俾政府搵人談判<br />\n每一個人既共識都係<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n而家solomon講咗幾句<br />\n就個個話去加泰集會會搞死場民主運動<br />\n係唔係代表承認solomon、美國係大台<br />\n第時可以交俾solomon、美國去同港府談判？<br />\n到時又係唔係真係「五大訴求、缺一不可」？<br />\n你地自己諗清楚啦..."},{"pid":"1b9e58cb02ac9b265b2aa71c6b262a10a8968110","tid":1670484,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f6beeab363c3e00bb4174546da1feecd5021d","tid":1670484,"uid":223598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"唔去 賭唔過"},{"pid":"140e8c3d8d8c474f8570ae24df4e432d505b481b","tid":1670484,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:09:49.000Z","msg":"佢出聲前，已經大把人反對啦，唔好講到突然反對咁"},{"pid":"8941ba1b15a0f3b4edd6820920b4d6022d5a9c13","tid":1670484,"uid":215717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"佢講道理比人參考啫<br />\n大台=有能力發動/代表大群群眾<br />\nBy definition除非佢call一個遊行有一班人動員出黎，否則佢唔叫大台"},{"pid":"1881b5f7e50b8d0da22bf25c12f2dfad7d43d711","tid":1670484,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"306f6beeab363c3e00bb4174546da1feecd5021d","tid":1670484,"uid":223598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"唔去 賭唔過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"去唔去個人自由，<br />\n只係希望大家既心態係點都好<br />\n記住要不割席，<br />\n唔好咁容易受人一言一語影響"},{"pid":"9b0e525755b17d1f67fd758716d670fe7145d408","tid":1670484,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco